    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Get your little ones moving with our Officially Licensed Kids Jump Rope - the perfect mix of fun, fitness, and timeless play! Features either Minnie Mouse, Hello Kitty, Stitch, Barbie, or Disney Princess.</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">Girls Kids Deluxe Jump Rope 7 Feet Hello Kitty Minnie Mouse Barbie Princess Lilo</h2>\n  <p>Get your little ones moving with our Officially Licensed Kids Jump Rope - the perfect mix of fun, fitness, and timeless play! Features either Minnie Mouse, Hello Kitty, Stitch, Barbie, or Disney Princess.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>COMFORTABLE MOLDED PLASTIC HANDLES - Easy for little hands to grip, ensuring hours of hassle-free play.</li>\n    <li>BRIGHT EYE-CATCTHING COLORS - Fun, vibrant design that keeps kids engaged and excited to jump.</li>\n    <li>ULTRA-DURABLE ROPE - Built to last through endless jumping, twirling, and active play.</li>\n    <li>ENCOURAGES ACTIVE LIFESTYLES - Promotes fitness, coordination, and healthy habits in a fun, playful way.</li>\n    <li>KID-FRIENDLY AND SAFE - Perfectly sized and suitable for children ages 3 and up.</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/usurper-products/72109/hQG0IC7y3OSQ79PabEzLdFZC3aWQjd-metaanVtcF9yb3BlX2RseF9wYXJlbnQuanBn-.jpg\" alt=\"Get your little ones moving with our Officially Licensed Kids Jump Rope - the perfect mix of fun, fitness, and timeless play\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>Color:</strong> Multicolor</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>Designed with easy-grip molded plastic handles, this jump rope is made for little hands to hold comfortably, so the fun never skips a beat. Its bright, vibrant colors make every jump more exciting and visually engaging, capturing kids&#039; attention the moment they pick it up.</p>\n  <p>Crafted from a super durable rope, it&#039;s built to withstand countless hours of jumping, twirling, and high-energy play. This classic toy isn’t just about fun - it promotes physical activity, coordination, and a healthy, active lifestyle in a way that feels like pure play.</p>\n  <p>Perfect for ages 3 and up, it’s safe, simple, and endlessly entertaining—whether in the backyard, at recess, or as the perfect birthday gift. Let them jump, laugh, and grow strong - one skip at a time!</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
